title: RealWifeStories - Vicki Chase (The Perfect Hostess) NEW 13 April
description:
Vicki Chase loves to throw dinner parties, especially for her husband's friends and co-workers. Her husband's employee Keiran knows Vicki is the perfect hostess... so she won't mind getting groped in the kitchen while her husband is in the other room. Keiran takes full advantage of his boss's wife's hospitality and treats her ass like an appetizer.
